Absolutely. A simple memoization decorator works great:

```python
def memoize(func):
    cache = {}
    def wrapper(x):
        if x not in cache:
            cache[x] = func(x)
        return cache[x]
    return wrapper

@memoize
def is_even(x):
    return x % 2

